%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-microsoft-ai-gpu-blackwell-cooling-wasteful-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBlackwell%20chip%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20demand%20for%20AI%20infrastructure%20continued%20to%20surge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20press%20briefing%20ahead%20of%20Huang's%20keynote%2C%20Dion%20Harris%2C%20Nvidia's%20senior%20director%20of%20HPC%20and%20AI%20infrastructure%20solutions%2C%20described%20Vera%20Rubin%20as%20%26quot%3Bsix%20chips%20that%20make%20one%20AI%20supercomputer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVera%20Rubin%20is%20designed%20to%20address%20this%20fundamental%20challenge%20that%20we%20have%3A%20The%20amount%20of%20computation%20necessary%20for%20AI%20is%20skyrocketing%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20told%20the%20audience%20during%20a%20presentation%20at%20the%20CES.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20added%20that%20compared%20to%20the%20Blackwell%20model%2C%20Rubin%20marks%20a%20leap%20in%20performance%2C%20with%20more%20than%20triple%20the%20speed%2C%20could%20run%20inference%20five%20times%20faster%2C%20and%20can%20deliver%20significantly%20more%20inference%20compute%20per%20watt%20of%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERubin%20was%20first%20announced%20in%202024%20and%20has%20been%20slated%20to%20replace%20Blackwell%20ever%20since.%20The%20early%20debut%20comes%20months%20ahead%20of%20the%20late-2026%20timeline%20Nvidia%20had%20previously%20projected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENamed%20after%20astronomer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-chips-gpu-names%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EVera%20Rubin%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20discovered%20the%20existence%20of%20dark%20matter%2C%20Nvidia%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release%20that%20the%20architecture%20is%20designed%20to%20support%20more%20complex%2C%20agent-style%20AI%20workloads%2C%20as%20well%20as%20more%20networking%20and%20data%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Rubin%20systems%20are%20already%20lined%20up%20for%20deployment%20across%20much%20of%20the%20cloud%20indus