f%20the%20Pentagon's%20new%20counter-drone%20force%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJoint%20Interagency%20Task%20Force%20401%20says%20stopping%20drones%20isn't%20about%20one%20weapon%20or%20system.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnato-watching-ukraine-ways-to-kill-drones-without-expensive-missiles-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecounter-drone%20fight%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20require%20a%20mix%20of%20different%20tools%2C%20from%20ways%20to%20physically%20shoot%20down%20drones%20to%20electronic%20and%20other%20non-kinetic%20solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20demands%20easier%2C%20faster%20processes%20for%20testing%20and%20buying%20systems%20across%20the%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20task%20force%20was%20created%20last%20fall%20to%20expedite%20counter-drone%20technologies%20across%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense%2C%20replacing%20the%20Joint%20Counter-small%20Unmanned%20Aircraft%20Systems%20Office%2C%20which%20was%20established%20in%202019.%20Since%20its%20establishment%2C%20the%20task%20force%20has%20assessed%20and%20contributed%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanti-drone-kits-headed-to-us-military-bases-amid-threats-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUS%20military's%20counter-drone%20arsenal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20forces%20at%20home%20and%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there's%20no%20one%20system%20they've%20found%20that%20can%20stop%20small%20uncrewed%20aerial%20systems%2C%20or%20UAS%2C%20which%20the%20task%20force's%20commander%2C%20Brig.%20Gen.%20Matt%20Ross%2C%20called%20%26quot%3Bthe%20defining%20threat%20of%20our%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20silver%20bullet%20for%20counter-UAS.%20There's%20just%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20Ross%20said%20last%20month%20at%20a%20media%20roundtable.%20%26quot%3BIf%20there%20was%2C%20we%20would%20already%20have%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20the%20task%20force%20is%20focused%20on%20a%20suite%20of%20technologies%20for%20layered%2C%20integrated%20protection%20from%20drones.%20%26quot%3BOur%20formations%20must%20be%20able%20to%20detect%2C%20track%2C%20identify%2C%20and%20defeat%20these%20systems%20anywhere%20on%20the%20planet%2C%26quot%3B%20Ross%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20requires%20us%20to%20layer%20our%20defenses%20by%20integrating%20sensors%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-marine-tech-turn-light-vehicles-into-drone-aircraft-killers-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ekinetic%20and%20non-kinetic%20effectors%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20battle%20management%20systems%20into%20a%20responsive%2C%20interoperable%20network.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228256%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20small%20drone%20hovers%20in%20the%20air%20at%20night.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F695c1c9364858d02d217c36c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20task%20force%20has%20also%20led%20exercises%20to%20train%20personnel%20on%20detecting%2C%20identifying%2C%20and%20taking%20out%20small%20drones.%3Cp%3EUS%20Army%20photo%20by%20Sgt.%20Wesley%20Domalewski%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20many%20defense%20technologies%20already%20exist%20for%20countering%20medium-sized%20drones%2C%20which%20the%20Pentagon%20classifies%20as%20Group%203%2C%20but%20more%20work%20remains%20in%20smaller%20drones%20under%20Group%201%20and%202%2C%20UAS%20such%20as%20the%20quadcopters%20that%20dominate%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20counter-drone%20problem%20isn't%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ejust%20about%20what%20systems%20are%20needed%20to%20protect%20service%20members%20and%20civilians.%20%26quot%3BThe%20technology%20is%20not%20going%20to%20solve%20this%20problem%20for%20us.%20We%20can't%20field%20a%20system%20that%20will%20stop%20every%20drone.%20It%20will%20all%20come%20down%20to%20the%20installation%20commander%20or%20the%20perso